flowchart TD
    START([New Project]) --> BOOT["install.sh<br/>Seed skills, rules, and memories"]:::common
    BOOT --> DETECT{Detect repo state}:::decision

    DETECT -->|Greenfield| GREEN["Greenfield Mode<br/>(Empty or near-empty repo)"]:::green
    DETECT -->|Brownfield| BROWN["Brownfield Mode<br/>(Existing code, tests, CI, or history)"]:::brown

    GREEN --> GINIT["starter-init (Phase B)<br/>Configure core-policies.md & seed templates"]:::green
    GINIT --> GMEM["starter-init (Phase B)<br/>Seed memories (constitution, security, PKB, heuristics)"]:::green
    GMEM --> GFEAT["Pick first feature<br/>(Route to /spec-requirements)"]:::green

    BROWN --> BINIT["starter-init (Phase A + B)<br/>Phase A: Archaeology subagent sweep & map debt<br/>Phase B: Bootstrap config & seed memories"]:::brown
    BINIT --> BREAD["Read brownfield-map.md<br/>Identify risk ratings before first feature"]:::brown
    BREAD --> BSAFE["Pick small, safe first feature<br/>(Route to /spec-research if behavior unknown)"]:::brown

    GFEAT --> LOOP[Guided per-feature delivery loop]:::common
    BSAFE --> LOOP
    LOOP --> SHIP([Shipped feature + KB compounded]):::terminal

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef green fill:#ebf7f2,stroke:#10b981,color:#065f46
    classDef brown fill:#fffbeb,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#92400e
    classDef common fill:#fff,stroke:#d0d7de,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d

    class START,SHIP terminal
